'''Laureate of the Empire'''<ref name="Galactic Phrase Book and Travel Guide">[[Galactic Phrase Book & Travel Guide (real-life book)|''Galactic Phrase Book & Travel Guide'']]</ref> (or '''Imperial Laureate''')<ref name="Despotica">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/ximweek02/index.html|text=Xim Week: ''The Despotica'' (Part I)|int=Xim Week: The Despotica}}</ref> was a great literary honor, bestowed by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] upon only the finest scholarly minds in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The author [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] received the title of Laureate of the Empire on two separate occasions.<ref name="Galactic Phrase Book and Travel Guide" />

